headline.print_headline: Serena Williams Gets Chance to Avenge Halep Defeat
headline.main: Serena Williams to Face Halep for WTA Title

lead_paragraph: Williams reached the championship match of the WTA Finals in Singapore by beating Caroline Wozniacki, 2-6, 6-3, 7-6 (6), on Saturday.
